com.digev.fw.log

Class LogLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.digev.fw.log.LogLevel

  • public class LogLevel
extends java.lang.Object
    Every logged message can have a level associated with it. That level is checked against the level configured for the log being used. Only messages with a level higher than the log's level will be written. The order of logging levels from lowest to highest are the following:

  • TRACE
  • DEBUG
  • INFO
  • WARNING
  • ERROR
  • FATAL
